```
flowchart LR
  subgraph Dev["👨‍💻 개발/소스"]
    A[Developer]
    B[GitHub Repo<br/>main / feature/*]
  end
  subgraph CI["⚙️ CI (GitHub Actions)"]
    C[Build & Test<br/>Gradle/JUnit]
    D[Security Scan<br/>(SBOM/Secrets)]
    E[Artifact Upload<br/>S3 bucket (app-bundles)]
    F[Deploy Trigger<br/>CodeDeploy]
  end
  subgraph CD["🚀 CD (AWS)"]
    G[CodeDeploy<br/>Blue/Green]
    H[EC2 ASG<br/>Spring Boot App]
    I[(Redis)]
    J[(RDS)]
    K[S3 (images/reports)]
    L[ALB]
  end
  subgraph Runtime["🟢 런타임/백엔드"]
    H -- "JPA" --> J
    H <-- "Cache / Streams" --> I
    H -- "Static/Export" --> K
    H -- "SSE" --> U[[Web/FE]]
    H <-- "Worker Jobs / Redis Streams" --> W[Custom Worker]
  end
  subgraph External["🔗 외부 연동"]
    X[SMS Provider<br/>Solapi]
    Y[(Lambda for SMS Callback)]
  end

  A --> B --> C --> D --> E --> F --> G --> H
  L --> H
  H --> L
  U -. HTTP/Web -. L
  H <-. callback .- Y
  H -. send SMS .-> X
```
